What you need to know:

Messi has won 16 of their 35 encounters to Ronaldo's 10, with the remaining nine ending in draws. Messi has also scored 22 goals in those games to Ronaldo's 19.The pair have only met five times in Champions League games, most recently in the semi-final in 2011.Barcelona got the better of Real Madrid with a 3-1 aggregate win with Messi scoring twice in the first leg.